name: Design Project Template
description:
Use this template to organize your design project and standardize file structure across your organization. Leveraging a predictable format allows designers and other disciplines to seamlessly navigate between multiple files and prevents things from being misplaced.


Key features:

  • Cover page
  • Project status
  • Project owner
  • Scalable page-structures & sections


Download it, make it your own, and share it with us on Twitter at @Starship
